lineCorrection(String) - Method in class exam.CSVParser

localize(double, double, double) - Method in class exam.PharmacyService
Filters the pharmacies returning only the ones within a certain range from a specified point described by x and y.
Note: latitude and longitude are GPS coordinates so it is needed a specific formula to calculate the distance between them.
localize(String) - Method in class exam.PharmacyController
Using a POST request it looks in the body for a latitude, a longitude and a range and through the PharmacyService returns those that are in the specified area.
